.row
  .columns
    %h2 Want to play live?
    %p
      Bacchus holds trivia every Tuesday night at 7 PM at 33 Second Street in
      downtown Troy. Use the stairs leading down from sidewalk level to the
      left of the main building entrance. Free off-street evening parking is
      available two blocks west in the garage at the corner of River and State
      Street.
    %p
      The team leading at halftime receives a free round of up to four drinks,
      and the winning team at the end of the night receives a $25 gift card to
      Bacchus (redeemable on non-trivia nights).

